  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you to all the players who supported <strong>Bright Sudoku</strong> before!<br>The new version of the game is now available, and players who purchased the game previously can update to the latest version <strong>for free</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on player feedback, we have removed the 3D mode in this version. (If you still wish to experience the 3D mode, you can continue playing the older version.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the <strong>2.0.0 Beta</strong> version, we’ve added the following features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note-taking system</strong> – You can now make notes while solving Sudoku puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hint feature</strong> – Tap the hint button to get solving suggestions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong> – A brand-new story experience where solving Sudoku puzzles drives the narrative.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Improved controls</strong> – Gameplay interactions have been optimized for a smoother experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievement system</strong> – Unlock various achievements through story progression.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you to all the players who supported <strong>Bright Sudoku</strong> before!<br>The new version of the game is now available, and players who purchased the game previously can update to the latest version <strong>for free</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on player feedback, we have removed the 3D mode in this version. (If you still wish to experience the 3D mode, you can continue playing the older version.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the <strong>2.0.0 Beta</strong> version, we’ve added the following features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note-taking system</strong> – You can now make notes while solving Sudoku puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hint feature</strong> – Tap the hint button to get solving suggestions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong> – A brand-new story experience where solving Sudoku puzzles drives the narrative.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Improved controls</strong> – Gameplay interactions have been optimized for a smoother experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievement system</strong> – Unlock various achievements through story progression.</p></li></ul>",
